  <cateringDescription><![CDATA[<p>Enjoy a generous daily hot and cold buffet breakfast.</p>
<p><span class="st">A free daily packed lunch and</span><span class="st"> English afternoon tea with sandwiches and cake is provided for all guests.</span></p>
<p>In the evening, the four course half board evening meal is served in the <strong>Alpterrassen</strong> restaurant. The menu includes a salad and starter buffet, choice of main course, and cheese or dessert buffet. </p>]]></cateringDescription>
