  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<p><strong>Komfort Twin Rooms</strong> are around 28m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a murphy bed). They have a bath and separate shower and face north.</p>
<p><strong>Superior Twin Rooms</strong> are around 28m² and sleep up to three people (extra bed is a murphy bed). They are south-facing with a balcony, and have a bath and separate shower.</p>
<p><strong>Junior Suites</strong> are around 35m² and also sleep up to three people (extra bed is a murphy bed). These rooms have a lounge area and south-facing balcony.</p>
<p><strong>Single Rooms</strong> are around 18m² and have a bath. These rooms have a double bed and face north.</p>
<p><strong>All rooms have:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>TV</li>
<li>Minibar</li>
<li>Tea and coffee making facilities</li>
<li>Safe</li>
<li>Hairdryer</li>
</ul>
<p><strong>General information</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>Check-in time: <strong>3pm</strong></li>
<li>Check-out time: <strong>11am</strong></li>
</ul>
<p><strong>Local fees and taxes</strong></p>
<p>A local tourist tax of approx. CHF 5.25 per person per night is payable locally (children aged 12-15 years pay a reduced rate of CHF 4.75 per person per night, and guests aged 12 and under are exempt).</p>
